docs {
  ## Update Unit
  อัปเดตข้อมูลหน่วยนับที่มีอยู่

  Updates an existing unit of measurement.


  ### Sample Body
  ```json
  {
    "name": "",
    "code": "",
    "is_active": true,
    "decimal_place": 2
  }
  ```

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "uuid"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-27T00:00:00.000Z"
  }
  ```
}

